====Usage notes====
In various branches of mathematics, the cosine of an angle is determined in various ways, including the following:
* The [[x-coordinate|''x''-coordinate]] of the [[point]] on the [[unit]] [[circle]] at the given [[anticlockwise]] angle from the [[x-axis|''x''-axis]].
* The [[sum]] of the [[real]] or [[complex]] [[power series]]<br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<math>\sum_{n=0}^\infty \frac{(-1)^n x^{2n}}{(2n)!} = 1 - {x^2 \over 2} + {x^4 \over 24} - {x^6 \over 720} + {x^8 \over 40320} - \cdots </math><br><br>where ''x'' is in [[radian]]s.

